Name: Tint 'n Ink
About the game: It's time to hunt down your rivals, discover the world of high-speed paint shooting. Let me introduce you to all the hectic content around the speedball, x-ball and recball inside Ink. Tint 'n Ink invites you to enjoy the best matches of this sport as an e-sport. From team strategies in 5v5 elimination matches, through recreations of real military secuences, to famous bomb scenarios. Learn and use the best tactics and techniques in the world, in quick matches with random guys and also on the major competitions. Get and upgrade your prefered markers. with all the attachments available for you! Markers manufacturers, Field Design Staff and Modders, will work hard to keep blowing your mind. Be sure to stay tune to get everything when it's out.
